reviewText: Really important to watch even months before conception. But even if you watch it a few years after your children are born, still fascinating and important! Bruce Lipton is incredible, intelligent and changing the world!
Every young couple should have a copy of this.

I continue to use this video in my teachings with respect to personal and professional wellnes. Thank you Dr. Bruce Lipton for your insightful and science based hope for all humanity.
Kae
